articles.title: Elena Rybakina Establishes Herself As Player of the Moment With Australian Open Win - Sports Illustrated
articles.description: The 26-year-old may keep a low profile, but her game is loud, taking down Aryna Sabalenka in commanding fashion in Melbourne.
